recipe.title: Kadhai Paneer
steps: Add Oil in a fry pan
Fry Paneer if you like fried paneer
Add Paneer at last and let it cook for 5 mins.

recipe.title: Cholle
steps: Add Onion and let them cook until they are somewhat red in color
Mix well and let it cook

recipe.title: Kadhi Pakora
steps: Make a mixture of lassi and besan
Add the mixture and let it cook for some time
Kahi is ready to be served
